      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 124,
      "start": 5253.0,
      "end": 5256.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "都能理解，但是确实没有办法，运力没有办法恢复。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 125,
      "start": 5256.0,
      "end": 5260.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然后因为南方动雨导致了很多电线其实它设备不足，供电不足，是断的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 126,
      "start": 5262.0,
      "end": 5268.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我们很多时候就像一个朴实，不善言辞，默默努力。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 127,
      "start": 5268.0,
      "end": 5270.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "看着有些笨拙的一个孩子一样。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 128,
      "start": 5271.0,
      "end": 5273.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那年吃过亏之后，我们后来做了什么事情？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 129,
      "start": 5275.0,
      "end": 5279.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "没有过多的去诉苦，也没有过多的去抱怨，没有去伸张。",
