      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 133,
      "start": 5285.0,
      "end": 5289.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那包括从那年之后，大家知道那年的事情真的太多太多了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 134,
      "start": 5289.0,
      "end": 5292.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "多到我们后来都，很难忘记那一年。",
