      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那年我初三。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 136,
      "start": 5294.0,
      "end": 5298.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我还记得我在操场上，操场上发现了，我塞在别人塞的老鼠洞里，我写的情书吗？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 137,
      "start": 5300.0,
      "end": 5305.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以大家能理解这个很多修建的大的工程背后的一个唯一的初衷，就是国泰民安呀。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 138,
      "start": 5306.0,
      "end": 5308.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就是让大家都能过上好的生活呀。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
    {
      "idx": 139,
      "start": 5308.0,
      "end": 5309.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "这个到顿顿的时间了是吧？",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 4
    },
